ng-[-0.005em]","children":"Films for the dark passenger — the love, the work, the idea that colonised you. The films here understand that obsession is just desire with nowhere to go."}]]}]]}]]}],["$","main",null,{"className":"max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-5 md:px-12 relative z-[1]","children":[["$","section",null,{"className":"border-b border-line","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-3 text-[11px] tracking-[0.32em] uppercase text-ink-muted font-semibold pt-10 pb-4","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block w-5 h-px bg-ink-faint"}],"Choose an emotion"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2 md:gap-3 pb-8","children":[["$","$L4","destructive-love",{"href":"/obsession/destructive-love","className":"text-[14px] md:text-[15px] font-semibold tracking-[-0.005em] px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 no-underline bg-white/[0.06] text-ink-soft hover:text-ink hover:bg-white/[0.10] border border-white/[0.08]","children":"Destructive Love"}],["$","$L4","creative-obsession",{"href":"/obsession/creative-obsession","className":"text-[14px] md:text-[15px] font-semibold tracking-[-0.005em] px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 no-underline bg-accent text-bg shadow-[0_0_24px_rgba(19,237,255,0.35)]","children":"Creative Obsession"}]]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"border-b border-white/8 py-12 md:py-16","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-[720px]","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-5 flex items-center gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"h-px w-6 bg-accent/60"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-accent/70","children":["On ","Creative Obsession"]}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-[16px] font-normal leading-[1.8] text-ink-soft md:text-[18px]","children":"At some point, the thing you loved became the thing you could not stop. The line between devotion and destruction blurred and then disappeared. You cancelled everything that was not it. You lost people to it. You lost sleep, health, perspective — and there were days you would have given everything and more. These films understand that the artist’s obsession is not a personality flaw to be corrected. It is a mode of being that comes with its own cost structure, its own private logic, its own version of grace."}]]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"py-16 md:py-20","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between gap-6 mb-10 md:mb-14","children":[["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 text-[11px] tracking-[0.32em] uppercase text-ink-muted font-semibold","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block w-5 h-px bg-ink-faint"}],"Creative Obsession"]}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-[32px] md:text-[44px] lg:text-[56px] font-bold leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.025em] text-ink max-w-[820px]","children":"Films for the work that ate you alive and still wasn’t enough."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-[12px] tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-ink-muted font-semibold md:text-right shrink-0","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"block text-[44px] md:text-[56px] text-ink font-bold tracking-[-0.03em] normal-case leading-none","children":"10"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"mt-2 block","children":"Curated films"}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"py-10 border-b border-white/6 mb-10","children":["$","$L5",null,{"films":[{"title":"Black Swan","director":"Darren Aronofsky","year":2010,"rating":9,"mood":"violet","story":"A ballet dancer's obsessive pursuit of perfection for the lead role in Swan Lake drives her to the edge of sanity.","why":"Creative obsession as self-destruction and self-discovery simultaneously — the terrifying intimacy between mastery and madness.","after":"You'll understand that some things can only be achieved by losing yourself in them.","direction":"Aronofsky uses horror conventions to get at